Name: Cube Defender 2000
About the game: Cube Defender is a small action indiegame. Laser blasts threatening your cube's existence? Let them come and render their petty attacks useless. Rotate a cube within a cube to show those pesky bolts who's the boss with three different difficulty levels. Each difficulty level has three stages, which you have to complete in one session.
